08 Quel fichier contient les clés RSA des machines autorisées à se connecter via SSH ?

Il faut premierement creer une cle RSA avec ssh-keygen
ssh-keygen
Generating public/private rsa key pair.
Enter file in which to save the key (/home/lol/.ssh/id_rsa):
Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):
Enter same passphrase again:
Your identification has been saved in /home/lol/.ssh/id_rsa.
Your public key has been saved in /home/lol/.ssh/id_rsa.pub.
The key fingerprint is:
SHA256:bAh3reoNMTXV/XLzTSu1DyYhI8MGk4DyhuYkGFVtuqo lol@lolilol

le dossier par defaut est le /home/USER/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
il peut etre autre si pendant le ssh-keygen vous en decider autrement.
